snippet.title: Johnny Depp lawsuit against Amber Heard?! AGAIN?!
snippet.description:
Just when CurioSips thought that one of the biggest Hollywood scandals of recent years had come to an end, a new chapter has begun. We are referring to the conflict between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard because now Johnny has filed a $50M defamation suit against Amber! Watch this video with your CurioSips family to find out about the alleged beatings, infidelities and other accusations surrounding this former couple! #johnnydepp #amberheard #elonmusk
